{{Orphan|date=November 2012}}

'''Gilbert Allen McKenzie''' (27 May 1915&ndash;26 May 1941) was a New Zealand disabled artist and entertainer. He was born in [[Invercargill]], [[Southland Region|Southland]], [[New Zealand]] on 27 May 1915.<ref name="DNZB McKenzie">{{DNZB|title=Gilbert Allen McKenzie|first= Maureen|last= Hickey|id=4m18|accessdate=23 April 2017}}</ref>

